# Implementation Plan: Student View Tutor Profile

This plan outlines the steps to allow students (and guests) to view a tutor's public profile, including their biography, stats, and published courses.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The tutor profile will be publicly accessible. We need to ensure that sensitive information (like verification documents or internal status) is NOT exposed in the public API.

## Proposed Changes

### Backend (Spring Boot)

#### [NEW] [PublicTutorResponse.java](file:///e:/edustream-be/src/main/java/sem4/edustreambe/dto/tutor/response/PublicTutorResponse.java)
- Create a new DTO for public display.
- Fields: `id`, `fullName`, `avatarUrl`, `headline`, `bio`, `videoIntroduction`, `totalCourses`, `averageRating`, `totalReviews`, `courses` (List of `CourseResponse`).

#### [MODIFY] [TutorMapper.java](file:///e:/edustream-be/src/main/java/sem4/edustreambe/mapper/TutorMapper.java)
